msgctxt "an7.82:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 7 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.82:0.2"
msgid "8. Vinayavagga "
msgstr "8. The Monastic Law "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an7.82:0.3"
msgid "82. Catutthavinayadharasobhanasutta "
msgstr "82. Shines as an Expert in the Monastic Law (4th) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
#. VAR: samannāgato → samannāgato bhikkhu (mr)
msgctxt "an7.82:1.1"
msgid "“Sattahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato vinayadharo sobhati. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, a mendicant with seven qualities shines as an expert in the monastic law. "

msgctxt "an7.82:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi sattahi? "
msgstr "What seven? "

msgctxt "an7.82:1.3"
msgid "Āpattiṃ jānāti, "
msgstr "They know what is an offense. "

msgctxt "an7.82:1.4"
msgid "anāpattiṃ jānāti, "
msgstr "They know what is not an offense. "

msgctxt "an7.82:1.5"
msgid "lahukaṃ āpattiṃ jānāti, "
msgstr "They know what is a light offense. "

msgctxt "an7.82:1.6"
msgid "garukaṃ āpattiṃ jānāti, "
msgstr "They know what is a serious offense. "

msgctxt "an7.82:1.7"
msgid "anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussarati, seyyathidaṃ—ekampi jātiṃ, dvepi jātiyo … pe … iti sākāraṃ sauddesaṃ anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussarati, "
msgstr "They recollect their many kinds of past lives, with features and details. "

msgctxt "an7.82:1.8"
msgid "dibbena cakkhunā visuddhena atikkantamānusakena … pe … "
msgstr "With clairvoyance that is purified and superhuman, they understand how sentient beings are reborn according to their deeds. "

msgctxt "an7.82:1.9"
msgid "āsavānaṃ khayā … pe … sacchikatvā upasampajja viharati. "
msgstr "They realize the undefiled freedom of heart and freedom by wisdom in this very life, and live having realized it with their own insight due to the ending of defilements. "

msgctxt "an7.82:1.10"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, sattahi dhammehi samannāgato vinayadharo sobhatī”ti. "
msgstr "A mendicant with these seven qualities shines as an expert in the monastic law.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.82:1.11"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

